Shoal Games Ltd: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















shoal games ltd
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Software
Sub-Industry: Application Software
Shoal Games Ltd. operates a mobile software developer and publisher. The Company develops rooplay, a game platform that empowers children to play, learn, and create, as well as bingo, video poker, and sweepstakes games. Shoal Games offers families a handpicked and safe selection of interactive games for a monthly subscription fee.




