Shoal Games Ltd.


            
            Shoal Games Ltd. is engaged in the business of owning and marketing a non-gambling social bingo game called Trophy Bingo. Trophy Bingo currently lives in the Google Play Store and the Apple App Store. Its a game play mechanics are captivating players worldwide. Shoal Games was founded on January 12, 1987 and is headquartered at The Valley, Anguilla.

            
